For /etc/make.conf, please note:

use -jX, where X should be reasonable for nCores of current system
USE flags must be tuned for your own system.

Profile: ~amd64, kde desktop

Cool stuff: Together with kernel: https://github.com/wangbj/kernel-config
The gentoo system can be used for:

- kvm host / kvm guest
- xen dom0 / xen domU
- hyper-v guest
- virtualbox guest
